title: Daz3D - Poser - 99 Daz Studio Props - The Office
description: A large set of props to fill any office space with a particular emphasis on an abandoned theme. There's pretty much everything you'll need such as chairs, desk, tables, computer, filing cabinets, shelves, books, pens, waste bins, litter, paper, awards and much more. This set is for DAZ Studio only
